incident_updates.body: Maintenance will begin as scheduled in 60 minutes.

We intend to perform maintenance on Saturday, June 10th from 22:00 PT to 02:00 PT on June 11th (or Sunday, June 11th from 05:00 UTC to 09:00 UTC). Customers in the US and EU regions can expect intermittent interruption to New Relic services during this timeframe.

In order to minimize impact, we plan to perform efforts in two phases and in the following order: (1) a phase where customers may experience irregularities for alert violations and notifications and (2) a phase where we anticipate various portions of the New Relic UI may be temporarily unavailable. 

Alert irregularities may include, but are not limited to, missing or delayed alert violations and notifications for various data types. 

All further updates will be posted here on our status page.
